before_start: Be sure to mix and autoclave solution I and solution II separately before combining and adding trace metal solutions and vitamin solutions. Store media in 4ºC. Note, Vitamin stock solutions amounts are per mL Trace Metal stock solution amounts are per one liter. Adjust amounts, as needed, according to desired stock amount.
